titleInfo.title: Farm Credit Services of Americ, PCA et al v. Haun et al
titleInfo.subTitle: MEMORANDUM AND ORDER - The Motion to Dismiss 40 filed by the Plaintiffs, the Farm Credit Services of America, PCA, and the Farm Credit Services of America, FLCA, to dismiss the counterclaims filed by the Defendants Brad Haun, Michelle Haun, Cecil D. Haun, Carole L. Haun, Carol Knisley, and Shirley Knisely, and the Motion to Dismiss 41 filed by the Plaintiffs to dismiss the counterclaims filed by the Defendants Joseph H. Page and Frances K. Page, are granted, in part, as follows: The Defendants' counterclaims are dismissed, without prejudice. The Defendants may file amended counterclaims on or before May 14, 2012. The objection 52 to the Motion filed by the Defendants Joseph H. Page and Frances K. Page is overruled. The objection 54 to the Motion filed by the Defendants Brad Haun, Michelle Haun, Cecil D. Haun, Carole L. Haun, Carol Knisley, and Shirley Knisely is overruled. Ordered by Chief Judge Laurie Smith Camp. (TEL)
